<SLUG> BC-R-RADIO-TECHNOLOGY-INNOVATION-ART-835&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
FCC RULES CHANGE WOULD ALLOW USE OF ULTRA-WIDE-BAND RADIO 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (EDS: Resending to add art note. No changes.) 
(ATTN: Ala.)  (ART ADV 13 : Graphic is being sent to NYT 14  graphic clients.
Non-subscribers 15  can make individual purchase by calling
888-603-1036 or 888-346-9867.) 
(mk) 
 By JOHN MARKOFF   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
