u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OCTUPLETS-BORN-HNS &LR;      12-20 0050
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-OCTUPLETS-BORN-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  Sunday, December 20, 1998
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
Editors: &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
OCTUPLETS-BORN(Houston) _ A story will move at 9 p.m., CDT, Sunday.
By T.J. MILLING. Questions, call Jake Doherty at 713-220-7674. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Houston Chronicle  &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
